<HEADLINE> Russian International Yanovsky Joins PSG </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, August 14 (Xinhua) -- Russian international Igor
Yanovsky, who helped Alania Vladikavkaz win the 1995 Russian
soccer league championship, has signed a four-year contract with
Paris St Germain, the French club said on Friday.
