<DOCNO> XIE19980814.0017 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-14 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Quartey Withdraws from WBA Title Bout </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, August 14 (Xinhua) -- Ike Quartey of Ghana has
withdrawn from his WBA welterweight title defence against Russian
Andrei Pestriaev in Nice on August 20, promoter Michael Acaries
announced Friday.
</P>
<P>
Quartey has been treated for chest pains in hospital in his
hometown of Accra and doctors have told him not to train for two
weeks, Acaries said. 
</P>
