barely a week when the task force solved another kidnapping with
the arrest of two suspects.
</P>
<P>
The suspects, who are all from Mindanao, the southern
Philippines, had no chance to escape when they were surprised by
the elite police force.
</P>
<P>
The task force was organized by President Joseph Estrada just
last month in a bid to fight criminal syndicates such as
kidnap-for-ransom, bank robbers and drug lords. 
