<HEADLINE> Results of ATP Championship Tennis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, August 13 (Xinhua) -- Following are the results of
2.45 million U.S. dollars ATP Championship in Mason, Ohio on
Thursday (prefix number denotes seeding):
</P>
<P>
Third round:
</P>
<P>
Vince Spadea, United States, bt 8-Richard Krajicek,
Netherlands, 6-2, 6-3
</P>
<P>
3-Petr Korda, Czech Republic, bt 14-Goran Ivanisevic, Croatia,
5-7, 6-4, 7-5
</P>
<P>
7-Yevgeny Kafelnikov, Russia, bt Scott Draper, Australia, 6-3,
6-3
</P>
<P>
5-Patrick Rafter, Australia, bt Todd Martin, United States,
3-6, 6-3, 6-2
