<HEADLINE> South China Province Making Progress on Major Projects </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, August 14 (Xinhua) -- South China's Guangdong
Province has invested 7.8 billion yuan in 31 major projects in the
fields of transportation, energy and water conservation in the
first six months of this year.
</P>
<P>
