nearing completion on three major projects -- the Guangzhou
subway, the Dahe reservoir with a storing capacity of 327 million
cubic meters, and the Taiyuan pumping station on the Dongjiang
River with an annual water supply capacity of 1.7 billion cubic
meters.
</P>
