in the army as well as the whole country.
</P>
<P>
At least 250 people have been killed and 5,000 others injured
in the two powerful bombings against the U.S. embassies in Nairobi
and Tazania's capital Dar es Salaam last Friday.
</P>
<P>
The 150-strong Israeli rescue team was sent to Nairobi only six
hours after the bombing attacks.
</P>
<P>
