equipped with specially designed equipment, including heavy-duty
balloons, pneumatic jacks and cutters capable of lifting and
cutting through iron, cement and other hard objects.
</P>
<P>
During the whole rescue operation which ended Wednesday, the
Israeli team pulled out 95 dead bodies and rescued three people
trapped alive from the debris. 
