was promised under the 1994 agreement. And the United States has
promised it will seek to make up the fuel oil shortfall.
</P>
<P>
Kartman is expected to press for a date to be set for a new
round of four-party peace talks on the Korean Peninsula, the
officials said.
</P>
<P>
The four-party talks, including DPRK, South Korea, China and
the United States, were last held in Geneva im March, but not
date was fixed then for their resumption. 
